descriptionHtml:
Try this new level I created. There's a lot to explore and a couple of quests to complete. It is a work in progress (WIP) so I am still working on it and finishing up some of the quests, but most of it is done.

There are a couple forts to attack, a castle, some caves, a couple of secret areas and more.

The entrance to this location is just west of Riverwood, just across the river. You can see the picture for more details.

If you have any feedback or questions let me know.

Cheers
author: Your Dad
